videos.description: Brady Manek, Armando Bacot and R.J. Davis help UNC go on a 16-0 run to build a big lead over Kansas.

videos.headline: Tar Heels take control in the first half with 16-0 run

videos.description: Ochai Agbaji, Remy Martin and Jalen Wilson come through with big buckets for Kansas on three straight possessions.

videos.description: North Carolina's Armando Bacot has to leave the game after rolling his ankle in the final minute against Kansas.

videos.description: Kansas erases a 16-point deficit to overwhelm the Tar Heels and wins the 2022 NCAA men's national championship.

videos.description: Caleb Love's game-tying attempt is off the mark for North Carolina as Kansas clinches its fourth national title.

videos.description: The Kansas Jayhawks storm back against the North Carolina Tar Heels, erasing a 16-point deficit to win the 2022 NCAA men's national championship.
